Algorithm: Online Voting System

Step 1: Start

Step 2: User Registration

Input: Name, ID, password
Store user details in database
Mark user as “Not Voted”

Step 3: User Login

User enters ID and password
If credentials are correct → go to next step
Else → show error and stop

Step 4: Check Voting Status

If user has already voted → display “You have already voted” and stop
Else → allow voting

Step 5: Display Candidates

Show list of candidates/options

Step 6: Cast Vote

User selects one candidate
Confirm selection

Step 7: Store Vote

Record vote securely in database
Update user status to “Voted”

Step 8: Logout

End user session

Step 9: Counting Votes (Admin)

Admin retrieves all votes
Count votes for each candidate

Step 10: Display Results

Show total votes and winner

Step 11: End
